The rooms are fantastic and my husband and I stayed in a standard room which was also very spacious with a great bathroom.	Our room was huge, we booked a standard room on the third floor and it was great, we had a huge cornor view out over the street.	We have just returned from a short 5-day stay at the Hotel America, which lived up to its reputation for being modern with great service and facilities.	I visited Barcelona mid December and found the hotel was again to a good standard.	You'd be hard pressed to find a hotel of this standard for the same reasonable price - we'll definitely stay there again next time we visit Barcelona.